%E3%80%8B%E8%A8%B1%E5%85%89%E6%BC%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%BC%94%E6%8A%80-210210486.html|title=《你的婚禮》許光漢的演技|publisher=Yahoo! 電影|accessdate=2021-07-03|language=zh-tw|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210704134109/https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E3%80%8A%E4%BD%A0%E7%9A%84%E5%A9%9A%E7%A6%AE%E3%80%8B%E8%A8%B1%E5%85%89%E6%BC%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%BC%94%E6%8A%80-210210486.html|archive-date=2021-07-04|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://star.ettoday.net/news/2012348|title=許光漢《你的婚禮》票房破35億！「虐心癡情男」台灣看得到|author=鍾雨璉|publisher=ETtoday星光雲|accessdate=2021-06-21|language=zh-tw|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210703133047/https://star.ettoday.net/news/2012348|archive-date=2021-07-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2021年12月，他受邀拍攝韓國雜誌「DAZED KOREA」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dazedkorea.com/fashion/article/1554/detail.do|title=시간을 자유롭게 오가며 감각의 인식을 확장한 허광한. 그 내면에는 아늑하고 심오한 감정이 자리 잡고 있었다.－HSU KUANG HAN|work=DAZED KOREA|language=ko|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211121164919/http://www.dazedkorea.com/fashion/article/1554/detail.do|archive-date=2021-11-21|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite new|url=https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E8%A8%B1%E5%85%89%E6%BC%A2%E7%99%BB%E4%B8%8A%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E6%99%82%E5%B0%9A%E9%9B%9C%E8%AA%8C-%E9%BB%91%E7%99%BD%E7%95%AB%E5%A0%B1%E5%A4%AA%E6%9C%89%E6%B0%9B%E5%9C%8D%E6%84%9F%E4%BA%86-000000181.html|title=許光漢登上韓國時尚雜誌！黑白畫報太有氛圍感了|publisher=Yahoo! 新聞|accessdate=2021-11-23|language=zh-tw|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211123073327/https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E8%A8%B1%E5%85%89%E6%BC%A2%E7%99%BB%E4%B8%8A%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E6%99%82%E5%B0%9A%E9%9B%9C%E8%AA%8C-%E9%BB%91%E7%99%BD%E7%95%AB%E5%A0%B1%E5%A4%AA%E6%9C%89%E6%B0%9B%E5%9C%8D%E6%84%9F%E4%BA%86-000000181.html|archive-date=2021-11-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

